    <h2>Distributed Training</h2>

    <h3>Data Parallelism</h3>
    <pre><code>Each GPU has full model copy, processes different data:

GPU 0: Model copy → Batch 0 → Gradients
GPU 1: Model copy → Batch 1 → Gradients
GPU 2: Model copy → Batch 2 → Gradients
GPU 3: Model copy → Batch 3 → Gradients
        ↓
    All-Reduce gradients
        ↓
    Update all model copies
</code></pre>

